{"tid":589732,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"其實小夫成日唔要大雄跟佢玩好正常","createTime":"2018-03-12T05:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T16:23:05.000Z","uid":108894,"like":54,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"56bbd2b4a3e5f685dda00aa52164abaa35ea8d0d","tid":589732,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:09:05.000Z","msg":"水又唔識游，咩運動都廢，遙控玩具遊戲果D又唔得，玩鬼屋嚇到腳仔軟，玩過山車又要畏高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多帶佢去靶場射槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果叫佢自己匿埋睇漫畫，玩繩，不如匿埋係屋企算啦，帶佢去都冇意思<br />\n不過小夫成日撇低佢得黎仲要晒命串9佢就真係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (有時佢一家旅行晒命連胖虎果D都屌7佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n自己好地地玩咪玩，晒乜撚呀晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 如果玩war game小夫一定求佢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，得大雄=得天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee42915b941e828273f0e649171ecad4fc919ec","tid":589732,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"34fbd4b89b1c6c241905dc5c1452fdd3f29d47b2","tid":589732,"uid":74479,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"想表達啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e642d4b607ab9c696fc4633ac4d64120a9cb00f3","tid":589732,"uid":27729,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34fbd4b89b1c6c241905dc5c1452fdd3f29d47b2","tid":589732,"uid":74479,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"想表達啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:42:12.000Z","msg":"樓主1999<br />\n冇重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0624ae3b3594de91ce9e6ab438df8d3830ea8f","tid":589732,"uid":15358,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34fbd4b89b1c6c241905dc5c1452fdd3f29d47b2","tid":589732,"uid":74479,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"想表達啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:44:35.000Z","msg":"樓主就係大雄 廢柴一條"},{"pid":"423a9d2a2f92cf1216349b9609affd38394c75ae","tid":589732,"uid":108894,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34fbd4b89b1c6c241905dc5c1452fdd3f29d47b2","tid":589732,"uid":74479,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"想表達啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:01:59.000Z","msg":"有D睇哆啦A夢嘅人成日屌小夫呢樣唔預大雄，果樣又唔預大雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係冇人諗到其實小夫帶住一事無成嘅大雄玩係好冇癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我係小夫都會一樣，但係真係唔會成日仲串9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7badad40b49e9f0c42fbe419bebd1d36e593e1","tid":589732,"uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f0624ae3b3594de91ce9e6ab438df8d3830ea8f","tid":589732,"uid":15358,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34fbd4b89b1c6c241905dc5c1452fdd3f29d47b2","tid":589732,"uid":74479,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"想表達啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:44:35.000Z","msg":"樓主就係大雄 廢柴一條"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"你似D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c76ff68490074adfbab9ec83266ef9a2a67bbb3","tid":589732,"uid":3594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"其實小夫唔識諗<br />\n搵個綠葉襯托自己係靜香面前威威"},{"pid":"c8040a1b0de8949a37f3ec564c18d4436b1e352f","tid":589732,"uid":56277,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"係時候回下帶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係雙方唔用任何法寶下，全盛時期既胖虎同出木杉聯手可唔可以打敗大雄？ <br />\n<br />\n胖虎同出木杉既強處相信大家都知所以唔講 <br />\n<br />\n以下講下大雄既能力 <br />\n神力：多啦A夢重129.3公斤，故事中大雄多次徒手抱，攬，推，甚至拖住多啦a夢飛奔 <br />\n<br />\n高速：多啦a夢最高速係129.3km/h , 大雄多次同多啦a夢逃跑時跑係多啦a夢前面，證明大雄奔跑既速度高於129.3km/h <br />\n<br />\n神反應：劇場版敵人多次近距離向大雄開槍都避得過，反應能力比neo仲高(neo都中過一槍) <br />\n<br />\n高速運算能力：有集多啦a夢同佢回到古代，當地人講出當時既距離計算單位，大雄立即可以將該單位轉換成公里並計出身處地方同自家既距離，而且玩花繩亦需要大腦運算同手腳協調能力，大雄只要係電視睇一次就可以立即模仿 <br />\n<br />\n神學習能力：上面提及過玩花繩&hellip;仲有無論多複雜既法寶，只要多啦A夢講解一次就能運用自如，甚至會改良用法令多啦a夢一吃一驚 <br />\n<br />\n神記憶：只要出現過既法寶，大雄都可以講出名稱同埋用法 <br />\n<br />\n高速回復能力：無論比狗咬，比人打，甚至高處墮下搞到遍地鱗傷，只要數分鐘就可以恢復，印象中大雄亦未出入過醫院 <br />\n<br />\n快速睡眠：唔駛多講，都市人羡慕既能力 <br />\n<br />\n總括以上能力，加上多次拯救地球，宇宙，大雄係最接近神既男人，究極胖虎同出木杉聯手有無一分既勝算？？"},{"pid":"83177bdbcee7309a46695d915061b16e03d872d8","tid":589732,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c76ff68490074adfbab9ec83266ef9a2a67bbb3","tid":589732,"uid":3594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"其實小夫唔識諗<br />\n搵個綠葉襯托自己係靜香面前威威"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:25:23.000Z","msg":"靜香咁(懶係)爛好人會成日安慰大雄之後屌小夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfdb6fcb2f5176c30e604509ee683c2ab6d3b91","tid":589732,"uid":45536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8040a1b0de8949a37f3ec564c18d4436b1e352f","tid":589732,"uid":56277,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"係時候回下帶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係雙方唔用任何法寶下，全盛時期既胖虎同出木杉聯手可唔可以打敗大雄？ <br />\n<br />\n胖虎同出木杉既強處相信大家都知所以唔講 <br />\n<br />\n以下講下大雄既能力 <br />\n神力：多啦A夢重129.3公斤，故事中大雄多次徒手抱，攬，推，甚至拖住多啦a夢飛奔 <